>I was wondering if a Stewart Warner gas heater from a Bug will fit in a 63 
>Panel?
>
>

With enough fabrication it will, but "bug" gas heaters and "bus" gas heaters 
were configured differently for different mounting styles. If that's all you 
can find, I would say that it would be worthwhile to make it work. 20K BTU's 
of heat sure does make a bus feel a LOT warmer!!

